These are the code examples for the Introduction to CUDA lesson at the 2018
Petascale Institute.

The documentation for that lab is here:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1HHtZsFhIMOWy_GCC9TeQWa_RKqu_cLDf6ykCghzgI0E/edit?usp=sharing

Please note this code is from the BCCD (http://bccd.net) and is used with
permission from its copyright holders.
